title: Hour 3 – Vikings RB Dalvin Cook and 10-year NBA Veteran Ryan Hollins Stop By!
itunes:title: Hour 3 – Vikings RB Dalvin Cook and 10-year NBA Veteran Ryan Hollins Stop By!
description:
Jason Smith and Doug Gottlieb speak with Minnesota Vikings running back Dalvin Cook as he stops by to share a major announcement! Cook opens up about playing football amid the coronavirus pandemic, Tom Brady winning his seventh championship and the instant impact that Justin Jefferson had on the his team. Plus, 10-year NBA veteran Ryan Hollins stops by to break down the impact that Anthony Davis’ injury will have on the Lakers!
